*****************Bootstapping**************

Note:-These all commands on workstation

Step-1 create chef account login to manage.chef.io

step-2 download winscp

step-3 connect linux machine by winscp

step-4 copy chef-repo folder to linux machine

step-5 check in linux machine ls

step-6 cd chef-repo/

step-7 ls -a

step-8 cd .chef/

step-9 cat config.rb

step-10 knife ssl check

Note:- launch one more Amazon machine node-1

Note:-node 1 key tranfer fo worksation chef repok folder 


step-13- knife bootstrap 172.31.41.20 --ssh-user ec2-user --sudo -i node-key.pem -N node1

step-14 Y

step-15 knife node list 

Go to manager.chef.io check in Nodes

NOte:-Need to move cookbooks in chef-repo/cookbook

Step-16 mv cookbooks/test-cookbook/ chef-repo/cookbooks/

step-17 rm -rf cookbook/
